data.displayName: Real Deal - Australian Gas Networks Central 2

fees.description:
A disconnection fee may apply each time we request to de-energise a property.
For further details on the information presented in this fact sheet, or the terms and conditions of the contract, please visit www.dodo.com/energy/terms-prices-and-regulatory-information.
A dishonoured payment fee may apply to payments we attempt that are subsequently declined.
A printed bill fee applies to each posted bill.
A reconnection fee may apply each time we request to energise a property.
Payments made via Mastercard or Visa do not incur any surcharge. American Express and Diners Club are not accepted as methods of payment.

gasContract.terms: See our full terms & conditions at www.dodo.com/energy/terms-prices-and-regulatory-information.
gasContract.variation: Dodo Power & Gas may vary your energy rates not more than once every 12 months by giving you notice of this change not less than five (5) business days before it comes into effect.

eligibility.information: The details presented in this Price Fact Sheet are for a Residential customer located in the Australian Gas Networks gas distribution zone. Offers vary based on distribution zone, and may not be available in all areas in Victoria. Further eligibility criteria may apply.

gasContract.onExpiryDescription: No Term Contracts apply in line with our Energy Market Terms and Conditions.
